Marty lives in 東京 near a place called 自由が丘.  There was a rumour that he picked that area just because of the name, since he is a 自由ソフト fanatic.  He actually lives in 緑が丘 so there is now another rumour that he was involved in the JFK assassination.  Believe what you want; Marty's sister believes that Marty is a 火星人.
